Package: poumm
Type: Package
Title: The Phylogenetic Ornstein-Uhlenbeck Mixed Model
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2016-12-20
Authors@R: person("Venelin", "Mitov", email = "vmitov@gmail.com",
                 role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions for fast likelihood calculation, maximum likelihood and 
    Bayesian inference of the univariate Phylogenetic Ornstein-Uhlenbeck Mixed 
    Model; Functions for summarizing and plotting the inference results; 
    Functions for simulation of univariate continuous trait evolution along a 
    phylogenetic tree.
License: GPL (>= 2.0)
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0),
    stats (>= 3.2)
Imports:
    ape (>= 3.3),
    data.table (>= 1.9.6),
    adaptMCMC (>= 1.1),
    coda (>= 0.18-1),
    foreach (>= 1.4.3),
    gsl (>= 1.9-10.2)
Suggests:
    testthat,
    TreeSim (>= 2.2),
    Rmpfr (>= 0.6.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
